    </ol>
    
    <b><i><u><h2>Amazing facts about the Plant Kingdom </b></i></u></h2> 
    <dl>
  <dt>Posidonia australis</dt>
  <dd>Largest plant in in plant kingdom</dd>
  <dt>Wolffia</dt>
  <dd>Smallest plant in plant kingdom</dd>
  <dt>Gympie-gympie</dt>
  <dd>The most venomous plant</dd>
  <dt>Ginkgo Biloba</dt>
  <dd>The oldest tree species that is alive</dd>
      
</dl>
    
    <b><h2><p style="color:yellow;">There are about 2.2 million identified species on earth. 
      Scientists believe that a majority are waiting to be discovered.Approximately 1400 plant species are listed as endangered in the U.S. Endangered Species Act.</p></b></h2>

    
